    <string name="title_0_2_0">The Information Update</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_2_0">
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Advanced Progress:&lt;/b&gt; Added support for "Step Progress" (e.g. 1 of 3) and progress bars with icons inside the notification shade.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Priority System:&lt;/b&gt; New "Island Behavior" settings. Choose between "Most Recent", "First Come", or a custom "App Priority" list.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Smart Filtering:&lt;/b&gt; Improved detection of duplicate notifications and grouped downloads.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Visual Improvements:&lt;/b&gt; Fixed layout issues with Navigation instructions.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Per-App Config:&lt;/b&gt; Customize Timeout and Floating behavior per app.
    </string>

    <string name="title_0_1_0">The Expressive Update</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_1_0">
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Major UI Overhaul:&lt;/b&gt; New Material 3 Expressive design with smooth animations.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Better Island:&lt;/b&gt; Text now appears on the right side. Added Green Tick for finished downloads.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Per-App Config:&lt;/b&gt; Select specific notification types (Music, Maps, Calls) per app.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Smart Filters:&lt;/b&gt; Blocks duplicate notifications and saves battery.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;New Library:&lt;/b&gt; Filter apps by category and sort order.\n
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;b&gt;Localization:&lt;/b&gt; Added Spanish support.
    </string>

